        <p>
            Please contribute to a better understanding of the OER movement and take part in the <a href="http://fluidsurveys.com/s/rcoer-stakeholdersurvey/">OER stakeholder survey</a> from <a href="http://www.col.org/">Commonwealth of Learning (COL)</a>. For more information on the survey visit <a href="http://rcoer.col.org/">OER Regional Consultations</a>.
        </p>
    </div>

</div>
